								<strong>Flowers Scene:</strong>
								<p class="mediadescription">An interactive demo showing different outputs that can be generated from the "flowers" GAP mosaic (simulated using a multispectral image).
<p>Requirements: <a href="http://www.adobe.com/products/flashplayer/">Adobe Flash Player</a>.</p></p>
							</td>
